en um die gewissenhafte und ambitionierte Anfertigung von Wundern handelt.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 7aHISTORY / Medieval.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package 2020z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2020z9783110704525oZDB-23-DEG0 cprintz978387997427640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311220903540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783112209035423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783112209035.jpg  a978-3-11-069627-1  DG Ebook Package 2020b2020  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2020  aZDB-23-DGGb2020